snippet.title: Johnny Depp REACTION To Amber Heard Destroying Her Own Career
snippet.description:
Johnny Depp REACTION To Amber Heard Destroying Her Own Career!
Amber Heard was not exactly the most well known actresses until she met Johnny Depp, because Amber Heard was doing various smaller roles until she eventually dated and married Johnny. Who at the time of their meeting was one of the biggest male actors in Hollywood. He was rocking various movies and Heard very much benefited from him being around her and boosting her up.
They were a Hollywood couple and it showed in various ways over the time of them being together. Amber Heard started to gain more attention in the public eye via her appearances in movies like Justice League and Aquaman and started to get more and more roles that other actresses would have loved to get, in many ways she was rising through the ranks.
